variables.name: S650ALARM::s650NotifyIndex

description: Alarm severity:
0 - clear alarm or event
2 - critical alarm (set, if non-transient)
3 - major alarm (set, if non-transient)
4 - minor alarm (set, if non-transient)
5 - report event (set, if non-transient)
variables.name: S650ALARM::s650NotifySeverity

description: Date and time of the notification.
variables.name: S650ALARM::s650NotifyDateTime

description: Description of this alarm or event
(from the SyncServer S650 internal alarm/event definition table).
variables.name: S650ALARM::s650NotifyDescription

description: The sequence number of a notification. Each notification OID
has an independently incrementing sequence number. These are
reset when the system is rebooted.
variables.name: S650ALARM::s650NotifySequenceNum
